    CONTROL type='Grid' name='VoiceGRID' bounds='2.00 1.00 216.00 240.00' parent='Grid Pane' layerMask='1'
    PROPERTY control='VoiceGRID' name='colours' id='0' value='none' # grid panel bg
    PROPERTY control='VoiceGRID' name='colours' id='1' value='none' # grid panel border
    PROPERTY control='VoiceGRID' name='colours' id='2' value='none'
    PROPERTY control='VoiceGRID' name='colours' id='3' value='grid_connection_line' # connection lines
    PROPERTY control='VoiceGRID' name='colours' id='4' value='grid_active_text' # unselected active module text
    PROPERTY control='VoiceGRID' name='colours' id='5' value='grid_active_bg' # active modules bg and all borders
    PROPERTY control='VoiceGRID' name='colours' id='6' value='grid_empty_border' # empty grid cell borders
    PROPERTY control='VoiceGRID' name='colours' id='7' value='grid_target_border' # border for target grid cell (when dragging)
    PROPERTY control='VoiceGRID' name='colours' id='8' value='grid_selected_bg' # selected module
    PROPERTY control='VoiceGRID' name='colours' id='9' value='grid_selected_text' # active modules text
    PROPERTY control='VoiceGRID' name='colours' id='10' value='grid_disabled_text' # disabled modules text
    PROPERTY control='VoiceGRID' name='graphics' id='0' value='none' # grid bg
    PROPERTY control='VoiceGRID' name='graphics' id='1' value='grid_module_bg' # active module bg: grid_module_bg
    PROPERTY control='VoiceGRID' name='graphics' id='2' value='none'
    PARAMETER control='VoiceGRID' port='Grid Structure' module='Grid' parameter='Grid'
